Package com.intellij.openapi.vcs

Interface CheckinProjectPanel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CommitMessageI, Refreshable

    public interface CheckinProjectPanel
extends Refreshable, CommitMessageI
    Interface for working with the checkin dialog user interface (retrieving the files included in the checkin operation, getting/setting the commit message and so on). The active check-in dialog can be retrieved from the using Refreshable.PANEL_KEY
    See Also:
    BaseCheckinHandlerFactory.createHandler(CheckinProjectPanel, CommitContext)
